#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifies <filename>Makefile</filename>(s) to add debug info"
msgstr ""
"Past de <filename>Makefile</filename>(s) aan om extra debug-informatie bij "
"te voegen"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>adddebug</command> <group><option>-k</option></group> "
"<group><option>-r</option></group> <group><option>-n</option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>adddebug</command> <group><option>-k</option></group> "
"<group><option>-r</option></group> <group><option>-n</option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beschrijving"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>adddebug</command> modifies the <filename>Makefile</filename> in "
"the current directory (and optionally in its subdirectories) to add debug "
"info (<option>-g3</option>). It will also remove optimisations (<option>-"
"O[1-9]</option>)."
msgstr ""
"<command>adddebug</command> past de <filename>Makefile</filename> aan in de "
"huidige map (en eventueel in submappen) om extra debug-informatie toe te "
"voegen aan het programma (<option>-g3</option>). Het verwijdert ook "
"optimalisatie-instellingen (<option>-O[1-9]</option>)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr ""
"Dit hulpmiddel is een onderdeel van het software-ontwikkelpakket van &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opties"

#. Tag: option
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-k</option>"
msgstr "<option>-k</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep optimisations (do not remove <option>-O[1-9]?</option> flags which are "
"removed by default)."
msgstr ""
"Optimalisaties behouden (de vlaggen <option>-O[1-9]?</option> niet "
"verwijderen, standaard gebeurt dit wel)."

#. Tag: option
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-r</option>"
msgstr "<option>-r</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Recursively search through all subdirectories of the current directory and "
"operate on every <filename>Makefile</filename> that is found."
msgstr ""
"Zoek recursief door alle submappen van de huidige map en maak aanpassingen "
"op iedere gevonden <filename>Makefile</filename>."

#. Tag: option
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-n</option>"
msgstr "<option>-n</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"compile without NDEBUG and NO_DEBUG being defined (makes <function>kDebug</"
"function> calls work)"
msgstr ""
"zonder gedefinieerde NDEBUG en NO_DEBUG compileren (maakt de "
"<function>kDebug</function>-aanroepen mogelijk)"

